        "action": "Urgently set timeline and provide funding for roads to be repaired nationally.",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government to provide a budget and and agree a timeline for all repairs and, until that has been achieved, a compensation scheme underwritten by national government, to prevent ongoing compensation claims against already underfunded local government.",
        "background": "Many of the UK\u2019s local roads are in a state of disrepair and this can cause very significant hardship in the form of excessive car repair costs to families and businesses, and lost productivity waiting for roadside rescue.",
